    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically stout example of BMW\u2019s high-performance engineering, featuring the S54B32 atmospheric inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. This chassis has received critical preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry remain precise. While the Titanium Silver finish shows minor road wear consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain remains tight and the rod bearings have been inspected. A mechanically sorted driver\u2019s car optimized for longitudinal and lateral dynamics.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
