    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The double-VANOS system has been inspected for timing chain guide integrity, and the rear subframe has undergone reinforcement to mitigate common chassis fatigue. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for precise turn-in. This is a driver-focused machine with robust compression and excellent power delivery throughout the rev range.",
